nes of extreme violence, and some dialogue was altered, thus creating the \"Not-Rated\" version of the movie. The original version was subsequently released on DVD following an online petition to have the original version released. It received a PG-13 rating from the Motion Picture Association of America (MPAA) for violence, the first animated Batman film and from Warner Bros. Family Entertainment to do so.\r\n\r\nMephisto Odyssey and Static-X contributed the song \"Crash (The Humble Brothers Remix)\" on the film's soundtrack, along with a music video directed by Len Wiseman featured on the DVD.","name":"Batman Beyond: Return of the Joker","name_cn":"未来蝙蝠侠：小丑归来","tags":[{"name":"dc","count":12,"total_cont":0},{"name":"美国","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剧场版","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"超级英雄","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Warner.Bros.Animation","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"蝙蝠侠","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"欧美","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"电影","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2000","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"漫画改","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"推理","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"漫改","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Bruce.Timm","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"科幻","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"无","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"DC.Comics","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"华纳","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"其他","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"未来蝙蝠侠：小丑归来"},{"key":"上映年度","value":"2000年12月12日（TV）、2002年4月23日（影院上映）"},{"key":"片长","value":"73分钟（TV版）、76分钟（剧场版）"},{"key":"话数","value":"1"},{"key":"imdb_id","value":"tt0233298"},{"key":"导演","value":"Curt Geda"},{"key":"脚本","value":"Paul Dini"},{"key":"原案","value":"Paul Dini、Glen Murakami、Bruce Timm"},{"key":"制片人","value":"Alan Burnett、Paul Dini、Bruce Timm、Glen Murakami"},{"key":"音乐","value":"Kristopher Carter"},{"key":"製作","value":"Warner Bros. Family Entertainment、Warner Bros. Animation"},{"key":"发行"